These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
City: rome, miami, boston, hamburg
There 4 different types of food: peach, potato, raspberry, carrot
1. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person eating potato##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
5. the person traveling to rome is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| City   | rome | miami | hamburg | boston |
| Food        | peach | potato   | carrot | raspberry    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, classical, folk, techno
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, fanta, hot-chocolate
1. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of techno##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking juice is the fan of metal##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
6. the person drinking juice is the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | folk | metal  | classical  | techno |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate    | juice | fanta | lemonade    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, horse, snake, hamster
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, magic-tricks, filmmaking, hiking
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
2. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an odd position##4
6. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Pet          | hamster | snake | horse    | cat      |
| Hobby   | filmmaking        | hiking     | skydiving | magic-tricks |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, soy-milk, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, rugby, surfing, parkour
1. the person drinking lemonade is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is parkour##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate | 7up | lemonade | soy-milk |
| Sport   | surfing       | swimming   | rugby    | parkour  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, surfing, water-polo, climbing
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, juice, 7up, almond-milk
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking juice is the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Sport   | surfing  | baseball    | water-polo   | climbing       |
| Beverage   | sprite | almond-milk | 7up | juice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, chestnut, brown, emerald
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, pall-mall, blend, oliveros
1. the pall-mall-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
3. the person who likes brown is in an odd position##4
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
5. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Color   | brown      | chestnut | emerald | apricot |
| Cigar   | oliveros | pall-mall     | ritmeester  | blend  |

