.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, jazz, ambient, trance
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, february, january, august
1. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is the fan of techno##1
5. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | techno | trance | ambient | jazz    |
| Birthday     | august | january  | november     | february |

