.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, woodworking, filmmaking, drawing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, skateboarding, snowboarding, cricket
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Hobby   | woodworking | reading      | drawing | filmmaking |
| Sport   | lacrosse  | cricket | skateboarding    | snowboarding            |

