.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, zinnia, marigold, tulip
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, russian, brazilian, australian
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
2. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
3. the argentine is between the russian and the person who growsmarigold##2
4. the argentine is in an odd position##4
5. the person who growsmarigold is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Flower   | tulip | zinnia   | lily | marigold |
| Nationality    | australian     | russian | argentine     | brazilian  |

