.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, fishing, gardening, woodworking
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, february, january, october
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby      | fishing       | gardening   | drawing | woodworking |
| Birthday   | january | february | october        | september    |

