.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There 4 different types of food: papaya, banana, apricotmelon, apricot
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, dunhill, chaman, apricot-polo
1. the blend-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
3. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the apricot-polo-smoker##1
4. the apricot-polo-smoker is on the left of the person eating apricotmelon##1
5. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person eating apricotmelon##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Food   | papaya   | apricot   | banana      | apricotmelon      |
| Cigar      | dunhill | chaman | apricot-polo | blend |

