.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, fanta, tea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, tiparillo, havana, dannemann
1. the havana-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the havana-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking fanta is between the tiparillo-smoker and the havana-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Beverage          | tea | hot-chocolate  | fanta  | cola |
| Cigar   | dannemann  | havana | aristoff | tiparillo   |

