.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-13::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, baccarat, game, blend
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, indonesian, polish, german
1. the indonesian is in an odd position##4
2. the colombian is on the left of the game-smoker##1
3. the indonesian is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
4. the baccarat-smoker is in an odd position##4
5. the indonesian is on the far left or far right##3
6. the polish is on the right of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| Cigar   | baccarat | bongani | game | blend  |
| Nationality     | indonesian   | colombian  | german  | polish |

