.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, apple, grapes, radish
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, azalea, daffodil, begonia
1. the person who growsdaffodil is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating pear is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating radish is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person eating apple##3
6. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Food   | grapes | radish | pear | apple |
| Flower           | begonia     | zinnia     | daffodil   | azalea         |

