.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, snake, dog, turtle
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, water, milk, lemonade
1. the owner of the goldfish is between the person drinking 7up and the owner of the snake##2
2. the owner of the dog is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Pet   | turtle | snake         | goldfish   | dog |
| Beverage   | milk    | water | lemonade | 7up   |

