.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, colombian, dutch, thai
City: marseilles, new-york, colone, boston
1. the person traveling to boston is the dutch##1
2. the person traveling to colone is the pakistani##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is the thai##1
4. the dutch is on the left or right of the thai##3
5. the pakistani is in an even position##4
6. the dutch is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Nationality   | colombian | pakistani | dutch    | thai |
| City   | marseilles   | colone  | boston | new-york     |

