.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, firefighter, photographer, entrepreneur
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, august, october, july
1. the photographer is on the left of the journalist##1
2. the photographer is in an even position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in august is the photographer##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
5. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in october##2
6. the firefighter is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job         | entrepreneur   | photographer | journalist | firefighter    |
| Birthday   | october | august  | july     | february |

