.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, helicopter, tram, bus
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, december, may, july
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
3. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4
7. the person who's birthday is in september is the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Transport   | bus | jet-ski    | tram       | helicopter |
| Birthday       | december  | may | july | september  |

