.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, black, lavender, amber
4 different pets are kept: lizard, guinea-pig, pony, mouse
1. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
2. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
5. the person who likes white is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
6. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Color   | black | lavender | white  | amber |
| Pet     | lizard      | pony       | guinea-pig | mouse     |

