.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, fishing, baking, magic-tricks
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, marigold, begonia, amaryllis
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
3. the person who growsmarigold is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who growstulip##2
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
6. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Hobby         | puzzles | baking   | magic-tricks | fishing |
| Flower   | amaryllis          | marigold | tulip         | begonia  |

 